oding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/doherty_photo_7-©Federation-Studio-France-Wendy-Productions_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/doherty_photo_7-©Federation-Studio-France-Wendy-Productions_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/doherty_photo_7-©Federation-Studio-France-Wendy-Productions_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/doherty_photo_7-©Federation-Studio-France-Wendy-Productions_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/doherty_photo_7-©Federation-Studio-France-Wendy-Productions_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/doherty_photo_7-©Federation-Studio-France-Wendy-Productions_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/PETE-DOHERTY">皮特·多尔蒂</a>新纪录片<em>《我自己的陌生人》</em>的预告片和发行细节已经公布。观看上面电影的完整预告片。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/pete-doherty-libertines-glastonbury-2022-interview-indie-sleaze-new-album-book-3255293">皮特·多尔蒂 (Pete Doherty) 在 2022 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 上表示：“多年来我一直是独立音乐的先锋！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-documentary-about-pete-doherty-to-premiere-at-zurich-film-festival-3490436">宣布将在苏黎世电影节首映的</a><em>《Peter Doherty — Stranger In My Own Skin》</em>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">Libertines</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babyshambles">Babyshambles</a>歌手的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-gets-married-two-days-after-confirming-engagement-3060855">妻子 Katia deVidas</a>执导，她还在他的另一支独奏乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/peter-doherty-the-puta-madres-album-review-2480290">The Puta Madres</a>中演奏。</p><p>目前，该片已宣布将于 2023 年 11 月 9 日在英国、德国、澳大利亚、新西兰、瑞典、瑞士、比利时、西班牙、荷兰、波兰、加拿大、爱尔兰和奥地利。 </p><figure id="attachment_3498060" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3498060" style="width: 1767px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3498060" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1.jpg" alt="皮特·多尔蒂新纪录片《我自己的陌生人》的海报" width="1767" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1.jpg 1767w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1-400x566.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1-800x1132.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1-696x985.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1-1392x1969.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DOHERTY-POSTER-JPEG-HD_2000-1-1068x1511.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1767px) 100vw, 1767px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3498060" class="wp-caption-text">皮特·多尔蒂新纪录片《我自己的陌生人》的海报</figcaption></figure><p>剧情简介将这部长篇纪录片描述为“跟随英国朋克歌手兼作曲家、Libertines 的传奇主唱彼得·多尔蒂 (Peter Doherty)，讲述他在人气巅峰时陷入毒瘾的深渊。</p><p> “导演兼音乐家卡蒂亚·德维达斯 (Katia deVidas) 历时 10 年，为这位艺术家拍摄了超过 200 小时的独家镜头。用多尔蒂自己的话说，当他从黑暗中重回光明时，他为克服内心的恶魔而激动不已。”</p><p>预告片由新的档案片段组成，一开始主唱不祥地解释了 Babyshambles b 面“The Man Who Came To Stay”中的一句歌词（“如果全世界都告诉你，‘你就是那个人’，我不服你不要相信他们，我的儿子”），然后浏览多尔蒂作为小报素材和阅读节头条新闻的片段，通过他通过爱和父爱的救赎。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-CLASH">《The Clash</a> 》的米克·琼斯 (Mick Jones) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/AMY-WINEHOUSE">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a>也在剧中亮相。</p><p><a href="http://dohertyincinema.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>查看参与影院的列表和门票详情。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="彼得·多尔蒂接受采访：“我真的不想死”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TqMP4ELtnmM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/peter-doherty-video-interview-2019-drugs-life-death-puta-madres-2480183">在接受<em>NME</em>采访时，多尔蒂谈到了 2019 年自己的生活回顾</a>，他说他“面临着一个巨大的年龄问题”。</p><p> “我从来没有承认过，因为我从来没有真正感受到过，但我听到你在那里这么说，我在想‘操他妈的，我真的不想死’，”他说。 “很长一段时间里，我的一部分只是认为，如果我真的把它扼杀掉的话，这会很有意义，而且一切都会容易得多。”</p><p>现在，多尔蒂<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-and-frederic-lo-drug-free-france-new-album-the-fantasy-life-of-poetry-and-crime-3143250">已不再吸毒</a>，并且<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-says-that-he-nearly-lost-my-feet-during-his-battle-with-drug-addiction-3194042">已经戒毒三年多了，“差点失去了双脚</a>”，多尔蒂也准备与 The Libertines 一起发行一张新专辑。本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-libertines-new-album-anthems-for-doomed-youth-track-by-track-first-listen-review-16186">鼓手</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gary-powell-confirms-release-date-for-new-libertines-album-3495496">加里·鲍威尔 (Gary Powell) 证实</a>，乐队自 2015 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-libertines-new-album-anthems-for-doomed-youth-track-by-track-first-listen-review-16186">Anthems Of Doomed Youth</a> 》以来的第一张唱片将于 2024 年 1 月发行。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="und" dir="ltr"> 21.09.30 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2665.png" alt="♥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/XR1FGVWOCN">pic.twitter.com/XR1FGVWOCN</a></p><p> - 彼得·多尔蒂 (@petedoherty) <a href="https://twitter.com/petedoherty/status/1445448936429273099?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2021 年 10 月 5 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>鲍威尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-gary-powell-new-album-steam-packet-uk-tour-label-interview-3287083">此前还告诉<em>NME</em></a> ，他的重点是乐队第四张专辑的“前进”。 “好处是每个人都在写作，”他说。 “显然，我们不会尝试重新发明轮子……但我认为我们可以把船推得更远一点，同时仍然带来观众在观看浪荡子表演时所渴望的同样情感完整性和活力的东西”。</p><p> Doherty 表示，当他们在 2019 年首次开始录制这张唱片时，乐队一直在探索新材料的许多雄心勃勃的方向，将其比作<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-clash">The Clash</a>分裂的“Sandinista”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/freestyle-rap-sandinista-pete-doherty-tells-us-whats-going-on-with-the-libertines-new-album-2482089">多样性</a>。</p><p> “卡尔想要用我们拥有的所有这些疯狂的想法来做一件‘桑地诺’的事情，所以我们将拥有所有这些自由风格的东西和民谣的东西，然后还有更传统的多尔蒂/巴拉特歌曲，”多尔蒂当时说。 “我不认为加里和约翰的歌曲是其中的一部分，因为它们是非常非常有力的歌曲。”</p><p> Doherty 的最新作品是 2022 年与 Frédéric Lo 合作发行的广受好评的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/peter-doherty-frederic-lo-the-fantasy-life-of-poetry-crime-review-3183674">诗歌与犯罪的幻想生活</a>》。</p><p>昨晚（9 月 13 日星期三）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pregoblin-joined-on-stage-by-pete-doherty-in-brixton-to-launch-new-single-footage-3497928">Doherty 与 Pregoblin 在布里克斯顿风车的舞台上惊喜亮相</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-trailer-for-new-pete-doherty-documentary-stranger-in-my-own-skin-3498052">观看皮特·多尔蒂新纪录片《我自己的陌生人》预告片的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
玛格特·罗比加入洛杉矶演员罢工纠察队https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-joins-picket-line-at-actors-strike-in-la-3498042?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=margot-robbie-joins-picket-演员罢工线Chris EdwardsThu, 14 Sep 2023 14:49:22 +0000 Film NewsNewsBarbiemargot robbie https://www.nme.com/?p=3498042 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罢工" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位“芭比”明星此前曾表示，她“绝对”准备好出击</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-joins-picket-line-at-actors-strike-in-la-3498042">玛格特·罗比 (Margot Robbie) 在洛杉矶演员罢工中加入纠察线的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罢工" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比 (Margot Robbie)</a>与其他演员一起参加纠察线，以表达她对洛杉矶美国演员工会 (SAG) 和美国电视交易协会 (AFTRA) 罢工的支持。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>明星于周三（8 月 13 日）参加了从 Netflix 工作室到派拉蒙工作室的 SAG-AFTRA 集会。有人看到她穿着一件超大 T 恤，上面写着：“SAG-AFTRA ON STRIKE！”，还举着一个黑、白、黄相间的标语，上面写着同样的信息。</p><p><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/strike-actors-writers-hollywood-when-will-it-end-3477098#:~:text=TV%20shows%20that%20have%20fallen,films%20have%20all%20been%20delayed.">好莱坞罢工！关于演员和作家抗议的每个问题都得到了解答</a></strong></p><p>在集会上，澳大利亚女演员萨马拉·维文（Samara Weaving）紧随罗比身后，她也举着同样的牌子。</p><p>由美国演员工会和美国电视和广播艺术家联合会组成的美国演员工会和广播艺术家工会 (SAG-AFTRA) 在与代表主要电影制片厂的电影和电视制片人联盟 (AMPTP) 的合同谈判破裂后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/why-are-actors-striking-in-hollywood-3468340">，于 7 月宣布罢工。</a>例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/disney">迪士尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">苹果</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">亚马逊</a>、华纳兄弟等。</p><p> SAG-AFTRA 和美国作家协会 (WGA) 工会都在寻求更好的薪酬、流媒体剩余以及在流媒体服务兴起的情况下防止人工智能技术使用的保障措施。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">嗨芭比！今天看到玛格特·罗比参加罢工真是太酷了。一定要感谢她来支持我们。她说当然，你在开玩笑吗？没有照片，但她非常好！爱玛戈特！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MargotRobbie?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#MargotRobbie</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/barbie?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#barbie</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SAGAFTRAStrong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SAGAFTRAStrong</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SAGAFTRAstrike?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SAGAFTRAstrike</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/sag?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#sag</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/filmtwitter?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#filmtwitter</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/wgastrong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#wgastrong</a> <a href="https://t.co/ISD2mHCY3L">pic.twitter.com/ISD2mHCY3L</a></p><p> — 乔什·布鲁门克兰兹 (@JoshBlumenkranz) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoshBlumenkranz/status/1702037393606590489?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 13 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">玛格特·罗比今天支持洛杉矶 SAG-AFTRA 罢工。<br /> <a href="https://t.co/JMe2EGbVtg">pic.twitter.com/JMe2EGbVtg</a></p><p> - Pop Crave (@PopCrave) <a href="https://twitter.com/PopCrave/status/1702117010971189652?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">玛格特·罗比支持洛杉矶 SAG-AFTRA 罢工<a href="https://t.co/Fesg0pCGk1">pic.twitter.com/Fesg0pCGk1</a></p><p> - 玛格特·罗比日报 (@margotdaily) <a href="https://twitter.com/margotdaily/status/1702052529289220552?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 13 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在 7 月份的<em>芭比娃娃</em>首映式上，在美国演员工会和澳大利亚自由贸易协会宣布之前，罗比告诉<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V3V3A9i2l7Y"><em>天空新闻</em></a>，她“绝对”准备好罢工。</p><p> “我非常支持所有工会。我是美国演员工会的一员，所以我绝对支持这一点，”这位女演员说。</p><p>近几个月来，其他许多明星也表达了对罢工的支持，艾米·亚当斯、弗洛伦斯·皮尤、科林·法雷尔、杰西·艾森伯格、莎拉·西尔弗曼等人都出现在纠察线上。</p><p>与此同时，乔治·克鲁尼 (George Clooney) 和阿迈勒·克鲁尼 (Amal Clooney)、道恩·强森 (Dwayne Johnson)、奥普拉·温弗瑞 (Oprah Winfrey) 和朱莉娅·罗伯茨 (Julia Roberts) 等人都向 SAG-AFTRA 基金会的紧急财务援助计划捐赠了大量资金。</p><p> 7月，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dwayne-johnson-makes-historic-donation-to-hollywood-actors-strike-3472840">约翰逊向该事业捐赠了“历史性”的七位数捐款</a>，但捐款的具体金额一直保密。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-joins-picket-line-at-actors-strike-in-la-3498042">玛格特·罗比 (Margot Robbie) 在洛杉矶演员罢工中加入纠察线的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《忍者神龟》创作者认为漫威和 DC 的统治地位正在减弱https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-dc-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-kevin-eastman-3497964?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=marvel-dc-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-凯文-伊士曼Alex FloodThu, 14 Sep 2023 14:40:11 +0000Film InterviewsFilm NewsNewsDCMarvel Cinematic Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3497964 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯文·伊士曼" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两家制片厂都经历了票房回报递减的情况</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-dc-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-kevin-eastman-3497964">《忍者神龟》创作者认为漫威和 DC 的统治地位正在减弱的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯文·伊士曼" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Kevin_Eastman_Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>凯文·伊斯特曼 (Kevin Eastman) 于 1984 年与彼得·莱尔德 (Peter Laird) 共同创作了超级英雄漫画《<em>忍者神龟》</em> ，他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/dc">DC</a>漫画最近在票房上的统治地位发表了自己的看法。</p><p>自 2008 年的<em>《钢铁侠》</em>以来，漫威电影宇宙由 32 部电影组成，全球票房收入近 300 亿美元，该系列还发行了视频游戏、电视剧、服装和商品。然而，它最近的电影表现不佳，过去四年里只有一部电影突破了 10 亿美元（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/spider-man-no-way-home-review-marvel-tom-holland-zendaya-3119256"><em>《蜘蛛侠：无路可归</em></a>》）。同样，在一系列表现不佳的影片之后，DC 聘请了导演詹姆斯·古恩 (James Gunn) 来负责对他们的作品进行改造。</p><p>当被问及漫威和 DC 的束缚是否正在放松（至少在漫画电影方面）时，伊士曼表示同意。 “在某种程度上，是的，”他说。 “这么长时间以来，他们都做得很好。我记得当<em>《美国队长：复仇者先锋</em>》（2011 年）上映时……克里斯·埃文斯（Chris Evans）作为队长完美地完成了这一任务，而且是以一种非常真诚和严肃的[方式]完成的，认识到[漫画]粉丝群的重要性……一直到<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/avengers-endgame-review-2479864"><em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战</em></a>》（2019 年）和一些电视剧。他们取得了巨大的成功，让我们所有的原创粉丝都很高兴。”</p><p>他补充道：“所以我认为现在应该去其他地区创作有趣的故事……其他类型的漫画电影还有很大的空间，你知道……我当然很好奇这一切会走向何方。” </p><figure id="attachment_3498002" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3498002" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3498002" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem.jpg" alt="忍者神龟" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_Mutant_Mayhem-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3498002" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Mayhem&#39;. CREDIT: Paramount</figcaption></figure><p> Eastman&#39;s own Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (TMNT) have experienced a renaissance at the multiplex this summer with hit animation <em>Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Mayhem</em> . Co-produced and co-written by Seth Rogen, the film makes use of creative visuals inspired by the comics which are reminiscent of recent blockbuster hits <em>Spider-Man: Into The Spider-Verse</em> and <em>Across The Spider-Verse</em> – as well as popular <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Prime Video</a> superhero series <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/invincible-review-amazon-prime-robert-kirkman-2908898"><em>Invincible</em></a> . Eastman thinks there is growing demand for animated movies and TV series in this style.</p><p> “It&#39;s an interesting combination of elements,” he said. “When I was younger, being called a geek wasn&#39;t a positive thing. Now, you have TV shows like <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-big-bang-theory">The Big Bang Theory</a></em> [which focuses on a group of scientist friends] and things like that have made it more acceptable as you see in the popularity of all things pop culture… <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars">Star Wars</a> , Doctor Who, Star Trek and the Marvel Cinematic Universe which is just so spectacular.”</p><p> He added: “So I think the, the acceptance and familiarity and the wide-spread acceptance [has led to the success of these films].”</p><p> In recent news, <em>Mutant Mayhem</em> star, co-producer and writer <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/seth-rogen-discusses-why-he-doesnt-want-to-work-for-marvel-or-dc-3475284">Seth Rogen explained why he he doesn&#39;t want to work for Marvel or DC</a> , citing “fear” of getting “frustrated” with lack of creative control.</p><p> <em>Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Mayhem is available to pre-order now on DVD, Blu-Ray &amp; 4K Ultra-HD</em></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-dc-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-kevin-eastman-3497964">&#39;Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles&#39; creator thinks Marvel and DC dominance is easing</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
